    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine mechanical and cosmetic order. This specimen is powered by the S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip M-Variable differential. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe carrier panel to ensure structural integrity under high lateral G-loads. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec, featuring aluminum control arms and refreshed bushings for telepathic steering feedback. Zero oxidation on the undercarriage; a turn-key example for the technical purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
