      "description": "Presented in pristine showroom condition, this vehicle is a collector-grade example that has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior features its original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or door dings. Inside, the cabin retains its 'new car' scent; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolstering wear, the carpets are spotless under factory mats, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in peak form, boasting a comprehensive service history with all scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by authorized technicians. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, and the matching set of high-performance tires has over 90% tread remaining. We welcome any independent pre-purchase inspection to verify its exceptional state. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
